sequenceDiagram
    actor Admin
    participant Frontend
    participant Backend
    participant Auth
    participant Controller
    participant DB

    Admin->>Frontend: Select Sales date range
    Frontend->>Backend: GET /api/reports/sales (Bearer)
    Backend->>Auth: Validate token + admin
    Auth-->>Backend: Authorized
    Backend->>Controller: getSalesReport
    Controller->>DB: Aggregate orders
    DB-->>Controller: Metrics
    Controller-->>Backend: Report JSON
    Backend-->>Frontend: Charts/Table

    Admin->>Frontend: Open Stock Report
    Frontend->>Backend: GET /api/reports/stock (Bearer)
    Backend->>Auth: Validate token + admin
    Auth-->>Backend: Authorized
    Backend->>Controller: getStockReport
    Controller->>DB: Find low stock items
    DB-->>Controller: Items
    Controller-->>Backend: Report JSON
    Backend-->>Frontend: Table/Export
